fields.physical_description: Design: miniature cards, 1in x ½in, printed in colours; set is in original casing and the slipcase still flat;  picture cards and jokers show photographs of Sylvanian family animals

fields.history_note: Sylvanian Families is a range of miniature character animals with a dolls' house and equipment, produced by the Tomy Company Inc.  The tradename is held by Marvel Comics.  The cards bear the copyright date of 1987 and the name Epoch Co. Ltd.
